 150, 205)\" size=\"120\"]\n\n<p>Với nguồn cung từ hai trung tâm phân phối phụ tùng, phụ kiện ở Miền Nam, Suối Tiên Ford có thể cung cấp cho Quý khách hàng những phụ tùng, phụ kiện chính hãng nhanh chóng, kịp thời, chất lượng.</p>\n[button text=\"Phụ tùng chính hãng\" letter_case=\"lowercase\" radius=\"12\" depth=\"3\" depth_hover=\"1\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]\n[section bg=\"60\" bg_overlay=\"rgba(0,0,0,.5)\" dark=\"true\" height=\"522px\"]\n\n[title style=\"center\" text=\"KHÁCH HÀNG\" color=\"rgb(45, 150, 205)\" margin_top=\"-60px\" size=\"120\"]\n\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[testimonial image=\"123\" image_width=\"121\" pos=\"center\" name=\"Mark Jance\" company=\"Facebook\"]\n\n[ux_text text_color=\"rgb(255, 255, 255)\"]\n\n<p>The overall use of flatsome is very VERY useful. It lacks very few, if any, things! I loved it and have created my first ever website Punsteronline.com! Best yet, flatsome gets free updates that are great! (and the support is amazing as well!:)</p>\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/testimonial]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[testimonial image=\"123\" image_width=\"121\" pos=\"center\" name=\"Mark Jance\" company=\"Facebook\"]\n\n[ux_text text_color=\"rgb(255,255,255)\"]\n\n<div class=\"e-box h-p2 -stacked -radius-none\">\n<p class=\"t-body h-my1\">This theme is amazing, you can customize EVERYTHING! The theme is a game changer for the Envato Market, cant wait for the future with Flatsome. Soo many good experiences from this, THANKS!</p>\n</p></div>\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/testimonial]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[testimonial image=\"123\" image_width=\"121\" pos=\"center\" name=\"MIRORIM\"]\n\n[ux_text text_color=\"rgb(255,255,255)\"]\n\n<p>Excellent work. Very good theme, No need support, works perfectly. Congratulations !! <br />Waiting for version 3.0. Very excited.</p>\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/testimonial]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]\n[section label=\"Simple Center\" bg_color=\"rgb(45, 150, 205